{"tid":1790972,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"無人既話唔該唔好搞開花","createTime":"2019-12-20T11:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T16:32:01.000Z","uid":64810,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ca84e27976f85490b3f43b9de0cc6e5c14e8c499","tid":1790972,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:38:56.000Z","msg":"我可以好肯定講 上次和你shop 沙田一役<br />\n有黑衫帶班後生去連城 之後有個帶call機既 O記就由衝入連城 成個過程都係只有3-4分鐘<br />\n<br />\n勇武既 唔好下下跟人 同你講真係鬼 <br />\n打殘勇武 熱心個班 呢場運動就會散 我係同意既<br />\n你去唔去開花 無人阻到你<br />\n但至少 多人多手足先做野 無人既話就唔好郁手<br />\n你地既生命係 好 撚 重 要<br />\n同個班 係咁叫人出黎開花既冷氣軍師 係連登出完氣拍拍蘿友走既人 唔同<br />\n<br />\n記住要有自己既思考同埋保護機制"},{"pid":"2fc5d077b5ef26ba67575e04a9f56f2e2fcf7d5b","tid":1790972,"uid":1891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:39:43.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n1221<br />\n721後嘅五個月<br />\n香港人有忘記嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccF7Pwj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccF7Pwj.jpg&h=a4c97012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XcqBbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XcqBbk.png&h=b08a4737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPEkp4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPEkp4G.jpg&h=82652877&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ab4c10ac1b9889cd89ed7934b72a89e4986aa8c","tid":1790972,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:39:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1b599528f20a5b4144f985aad66aebd9ecf3f58","tid":1790972,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30688364746b5aede49bd331e39907a9a26c77e","tid":1790972,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy